  ID: MenAtArms2
  Name: Alfonse, Sicilian pikeman
  Icon: {fileID: 460225133, guid: 969acaabd3c81e14c9c953a67b21cef1, type: 3}
  Description: 'He enlisted because pike drills promised structure; civilian life
    never did. A cannon blast threw him off the rampart, and his ribs folded inward
    like kicked lattice. He breathes in gurgles.


    Treatment: There is no cutting
    here. You bind his torso tight with cloth and brace him upright. Every breath
    is shallow; too deep and he drowns in blood. You can only watch.


    Requires:
    2 Bandages'
  slotNumber: 1
